ZH: 我每周末在家里打扫。
EN: I clean the house every weekend.

ZH: 她正在打扫客厅。
EN: She is cleaning the living room.

ZH: 你可以帮我打扫卧室吗？
EN: Can you help me clean the bedroom?

ZH: 爸爸经常打扫车库。
EN: Dad often cleans the garage.

ZH: 妈妈正在打扫厨房。
EN: Mom is cleaning the kitchen.

ZH: 我们需要打扫浴室。
EN: We need to clean the bathroom.

ZH: 他们负责打扫学校的走廊。
EN: They are responsible for cleaning the school hallways.

ZH: 昨天我花了两个小时打扫房子。
EN: I spent two hours cleaning the house yesterday.

ZH: 今天我要把办公室打扫干净。
EN: Today I will clean the office thoroughly.

ZH: 打扫完后，屋子变得整洁了。
EN: After cleaning, the room became tidy.

ZH: 不要忘记打扫冰箱里的食物残渣。
EN: Don't forget to clean up the food residue in the fridge.

ZH: 她下午要打扫客厅。
EN: She will clean the living room in the afternoon.

ZH: 打扫卫生是我们的责任。
EN: Cleaning up is our responsibility.

ZH: 房客们定期打扫公共区域。
EN: The tenants clean the common areas regularly.

ZH: 请您打扫好后离开。
EN: Please leave after you have cleaned up.

ZH: 请确保打扫得彻底。
EN: Please make sure to clean thoroughly.

ZH: 他邀请了朋友帮忙打扫车库。
EN: He invited friends to help clean the garage.

ZH: 我会打扫自己的房间。
EN: I will clean my own room.

ZH: 打扫工作是一件重要却常被忽视的事。
EN: Cleaning is an important but often overlooked task.
